Protect It does not knowingly collect data from children under the age of 13. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected such data, we will promptly delete it.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Continued use of Protect It after any changes indicates your acceptance of the updated terms. Please review this Privacy Policy regularly for any updates.
